{"word":"ὁμόφωνος","slug":"ὁμόφωνος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ὁμόφωνος</b></el> <el>(ὁμό-φωνος, ον,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:φωνή'><el>φωνή</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>speaking the same language with</i> others, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>of the same sound</i> or <i>tone, in unison with</i>, <el>τινι</el> <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}